,{"s":23.4,"e":25.62,"text":"They said, \"Who gave you that? Who let you in?\""},{"s":25.68,"e":27.42,"text":"He shrugged like it was nothing, played dumb again"},{"s":27.42,"e":29.24,"text":"But the crowd went still when the hook hit right"},{"s":29.24,"e":31,"text":"Like a stolen sunrise in the dead of night"},{"s":31,"e":32.8,"text":"Then the clocks started choking"},{"s":32.92,"e":34.32,"text":"Walls came apart"},{"s":34.32,"e":35.94,"text":"Footsteps from tomorrow"},{"s":36.12,"e":37.98,"text":"Already in the dark"},{"s":38.02,"e":39.82,"text":"They looked at him sideways"},{"s":39.96,"e":41.52,"text":"Like he broke the law"},{"s":41.52,"e":43.66,"text":"He said, \"I just wrote it\""},{"s":43.72,"e":45.23,"text":"Now they wanted it back, all"},{"s":45.58,"e":49.5,"text":"He got in trouble with time travelers"},{"s":49.5,"e":52.86,"text":"Trouble with time travelers"},{"s":52.86,"e":60.48,"text":"They came for the song, for the song, for the song"},{"s":60.4,"e":64.3,"text":"He got in trouble with time travelers"},{"s":64.3,"e":67.82,"text":"Trouble with time travelers"},{"s":67.82,"e":75.24,"text":"Now every tomorrow says he did them wrong (he did them wrong)"},{"s":75.74,"e":78.02,"text":"One wore a coat made of mirror thread"},{"s":78.02,"e":79.8,"text":"One had a scar where the date should've bled"},{"s":79.78,"e":81.72,"text":"They said, \"That melody's ours in a year or two"},{"s":81.72,"e":83.54,"text":"You can't just drop it like the way you do\""},{"s":83.54,"e":85.42,"text":"He said, \"Man, I don't know what you want from me"},{"s":85.42,"e":87.24,"text":"I just made a record, set the future free\""},{"s":87.24,"e":89.18,"text":"But they traced his steps with a silver pen"},{"s":89.18,"e":91.36,"text":"Said the whole timeline split when the beat came in"},{"s":91.36,"e":91.7,"text":"Then the clocks started choking"},{"s":92.22,"e":93.64,"text":"Walls came apart"},{"s":93.96,"e":95.44,"text":"Footsteps from tomorrow"},{"s":95.7,"e":97.38,"text":"Already in the dark"},{"s":97.38,"e":99.24,"text":"They looked at him sideways"},{"s":99.38,"e":101.1,"text":"Like he broke the law"},{"s":101.02,"e":103.1,"text":"He said, \"I just wrote it\""},{"s":103.2,"e":104.46,"text":"Now they wanted it back, all"},{"s":104.38,"e":108.58,"text":"He got in trouble with time travelers"},{"s":108.58,"e":112.44,"text":"Trouble with time travelers"},{"s":112.44,"e":118.1,"text":"They came for the song, for the song, for the song"},{"s":119.6,"e":123.78,"text":"He got in trouble with time travelers"},{"s":123.78,"e":126.94,"text":"Trouble with time travelers"},{"s":127.12,"e":134.5,"text":"Now every tomorrow says he did them wrong (he did them wrong)"},{"s":135.18,"e":137.74,"text":"Now he hides where the seconds bend"},{"s":137.74,"e":139.92,"text":"Keeps one eye open for the future men"},{"s":139.92,"e":141.32,"text":"If they knock, he won't let 'em in"},{"s":141.32,"e":143.5,"text":"He'll drop that track and disappear again"},{"s":143.5,"e":145.32,"text":"Tick-tock on the window"},{"s":145.28,"e":147.06,"text":"Black vans in the rain"},{"s":147.06,"e":148.98,"text":"He laughs when they call him"},{"s":148.98,"e":150.78,"text":"Then does it all again"},{"s":150.78,"e":155.38,"text":"He got in trouble with time travelers"},{"s":156.08,"e":158.86,"text":"Trouble with time travelers"},{"s":158.86,"e":164.52,"text":"They came for the song, for the song, for the song"},{"s":166.54,"e":170.22,"text":"He got in trouble with time travelers"},{"s":170.22,"e":173.7,"text":"Trouble with time travelers"},{"s":173.7,"e":191.14,"text":"Now every tomorrow says he did them wrong (he did them wrong)"}],"duration":191.12,"source":"whisper-aligned","generatedAt":"2026-05-30T01:57:12.492Z","stats":{"whisperWords":413,"polishedWords":411,"matched":382,"matchRate":0.929}}